sentences.sentence: We studied relationships among body size, clutch size, and egg size and female reproductive characteristics in five species of oviparous colubrid snakes from Zhoushan islands, Zhejiang, China.
sentences.translation: 阐明五种游蛇科动物雌体大小、窝卵数和卵大小之间的关系和雌性繁殖特征的种间差异。
